## Idle Detection System (dualgpuopt/tray.py)
- GPU utilization monitoring with configurable thresholds
- Sustained low utilization detection algorithm
- Alert mechanism for underutilized GPU resources
- Configurable idle time threshold in minutes
- Default utilization threshold of 30%

